### Get all users
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users

### Get user by ID
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users/1

### Create new user
POST https://localhost:7000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### Get all lessons
GET https://localhost:7000/api/lessons

### Get lesson by ID
GET https://localhost:7000/api/lessons/1

### Create new lesson
POST https://localhost:7000/api/lessons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Introduction to Programming",
  "content": "Learn the basics of programming concepts.",
  "category": "Programming",
  "difficulty": 1
}

### Get all progress records
GET https://localhost:7000/api/progress

### Get progress by user ID
GET https://localhost:7000/api/progress/user/1

### Create progress record
POST https://localhost:7000/api/progress
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "lessonId": 1,
  "completed": true,
  "score": 85
}
